Class Enemy

  • java.lang.Object
    • nachogame.SpaceObject
      • nachogame.Enemy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TacoBoss

    public class Enemy
extends SpaceObject
    This is a Enemy class for the space nacho game. The class will perform the graphic resize for enemies, detect collisions for the enemies, and determine if the enemies are destroyed or not.
    Version:
    10-24-2017
    Author:
    Jon DeWent, Cheng Li, Ryan Bassor

        public boolean collide(Projectile other)
